cat << EOF
DataObject performs 2 tasks:
1. Builds SQL statements based on the objects
vars and the builder methods.
2. acts as a datastore for a table row.
The core class is designed to be extended for
each of your tables so that you put the
data logic inside the data classes.
included is a Generator to make your
configuration files and your base classes.
EOF

